{"tid":133873,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓尿PH值測試","createTime":"2017-02-25T04:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T02:12:36.000Z","uid":21654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"339643433c99a7f822a75ed1a2949698c9374299","tid":133873,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T04:39:18.000Z","msg":"頭去左金魚街買PH試紙<br />\n大陸野20蚊細細盒都有好多張<br />\n番到屋企見到兩隻貓已屙尿不過撈埋左<br />\n即係拎嚟試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喺6-7之間，正常無事<br />\n下次有機會先續隻驗<br />\n有無貓奴都試下？尤其食緊尿道處方糧可以check check，正常番就唔好再食，貓尿太酸一樣會生石<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/25/123406_5fae4f7e00e6fa277ef1e770069f03e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F25%2F123406_5fae4f7e00e6fa277ef1e770069f03e7.jpg&h=e3a527d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1bafa4eba44712e1e92aa3d79b3310db53e908cd","tid":133873,"uid":4681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T08:11:53.000Z","msg":"你點草到佢啲尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ee12025a8f446939657313fa7f001c64c13f60","tid":133873,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T13:16:37.000Z","msg":"用緊雙層砂盆，上格薄鋪木砂<br />\n吸唔晒就流落下層"},{"pid":"5ef25200cfe738ef9cacd6bc27bb9467cffd0cea","tid":133873,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T02:12:36.000Z","msg":"原來金魚街有得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}